datepicker.name: datepicker
datepicker.description: A component that enables the user to select a date or date range.

propList.Name: allowClear
propList.Description: Whether to show clear button

propList.Name: autoFocus
propList.Description: If get focus when component mounted

propList.Name: bordered
propList.Description: Whether has border style

propList.Name: className
propList.Description: The picker className

propList.Name: dateRender
propList.Description: Custom rendering function for date cells

propList.Name: disabled
propList.Description: Determine whether the DatePicker is disabled

propList.Name: disabledDate
propList.Description: Specify the date that cannot be selected

propList.Name: dropdownClassName
propList.Description: To customize the className of the popup calendar

propList.Name: getPopupContainer
propList.Description: To set the container of the floating layer, while the default is to create a div element in body

propList.Name: inputReadOnly
propList.Description: Set the readonly attribute of the input tag (avoids virtual keyboard on touch devices)

propList.Name: locale
propList.Description: Localization configuration

propList.Name: mode
propList.Description: The picker panel modeï¼ˆ Cannot select year or month anymore? )

propList.Name: open
propList.Description: The open state of picker

propList.Name: panelRender
propList.Description: Customize panel render

propList.Name: picker
propList.Description: Set picker type

propList.Name: placeholder
propList.Description: The placeholder of date input

propList.Name: popupStyle
propList.Description: To customize the style of the popup calendar

propList.Name: size
propList.Description: To determine the size of the input box, the height of large and small, are 40px and 24px respectively, while default size is 32px

propList.Name: style
propList.Description: To customize the style of the input box

propList.Name: suffixIcon
propList.Description: The custom suffix icon

propList.Name: onOpenChange
propList.Description: Callback function, can be executed whether the popup calendar is popped up or closed

propList.Name: onPanelChange
propList.Description: Callback when picker panel mode is changed
